These are simple samples of Nesla programs.

   _ajax.ns       included file used to add AJAX functions
   _cards.ns      included file used to define playing cards
   ansi.ns        simple ANSI codes
   current.ns     download latest test release of Nesla (via http)
   dirhash.ns     create md5 hashes of all files in a directory (recursively)
   factorial.ns   calculates the factorial of a number
   hello.ns       the first program in every language
   ht-bj.ns       blackjack game for web servers using ajax (kinda)
   ht-cms.ns      A _very_ crude Content Management System
   ht-index.ns    html file listing script
   ht-poker.ns    poker game for web servers using ajax (kinda)
   ht-shell.ns    simple shell for web servers
   httpd.ns       functioning demo web server
   lis.ns         psychiatry for the lonely and desperate
   lis-l.ns       language file for lis.ns
   litemeld.ns    meld all required source files for neslite into a single c file
   popclass.ns    pop3 client to sync mail account with a local dir
   smtpc.ns       smtp client
   sqrt.ns        simple square root algorithm
   src2html.ns    converts scripts to html
